{"tid":2141003,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［化驗賣港］支那全面入侵香港醫務化驗，醫務化驗師委員會係咪死撚咗？","createTime":"2020-08-05T11:17:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T08:54:46.000Z","uid":137078,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8d165166e8ea438e1ce7061d2d01e1aaa4b49138","tid":2141003,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:17:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/BGWLNR63BPEAFVFBSR7TUKOLME/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FBGWLNR63BPEAFVFBSR7TUKOLME%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=d9e8590a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2FBGWLNR63BPEAFVFBSR7TUKOLME%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post&h=968a5f66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/BGWLNR63BPEAFVFBSR7TUKOLME/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post</a><br />\nSource：Apple Daily<br />\n<br />\n/本港一直採取單樣本化驗方式，但內地「核酸檢測支援隊」成員近日向官媒直言希望在港「落實」混合樣本化驗。本港醫務化驗所總會主席李偉振昨首度提議，改為採用混合樣本法提升檢測量，即把數份樣本混在一起化驗，若呈陽性才覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n不過，有資深化驗師指混合數份樣本，難找到弱陽性或病毒量低的個案，「呢啲可能係隱形病人，係最需要搵出嘅人」，變相「白做」。雖然內地曾嘗試「五合一」或「十合一」混和樣本化驗，但要本港改變「行規」，猶如賭上化驗行業的聲譽。<span class=\"red\">武漢亞心總醫院董事長謝俊明於訪問時聲稱，已獲港府同意，調派亞心總醫院20至30名化驗師來港協助，指最快本月15日可開展工作。/</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/4AF334GTUPDJKQXTGKTQFLS2WQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2F4AF334GTUPDJKQXTGKTQFLS2WQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F98yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=8384b48e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200805%2F4AF334GTUPDJKQXTGKTQFLS2WQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post&h=eb88feaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200805/4AF334GTUPDJKQXTGKTQFLS2WQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post</a>"},{"pid":"f93900631a90d8e0b96ae8e5158c1031b78a68e4","tid":2141003,"uid":362827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:18:49.000Z","msg":"班友都冇聲出點解仲要幫佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c86ce4c21e521e5fd66f7314aaba0ae5c129947","tid":2141003,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:22:58.000Z","msg":"醫療界毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52079bbd74b3bcb3b5f6b375358bf7b6292cec1d","tid":2141003,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T14:04:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa13f3c0e3f3cb2360791634286af1d7d4d7e2d6","tid":2141003,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T05:54:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b57280006536cbcc3143bda32fc9da8f3927b765","tid":2141003,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T05:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d105e8cbe57b6764bd2eff9394bdd489444cfea","tid":2141003,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:43:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"299e28f3449fc723451ec20691bf288dbacced0b","tid":2141003,"uid":41768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:45:55.000Z","msg":"佢地都準備失業啦 比大陸取代緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a4682d8172c2c7c01e42987d75ccfa6ef101d7","tid":2141003,"uid":105958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:52:56.000Z","msg":"辛辛苦苦讀個mlt <br />\n9日俾大陸人取代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要係驗車既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知仲以為得大陸有化驗師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e981d6fbfe595958bfa56f7af156a86636e24a","tid":2141003,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:49:17.000Z","msg":"特首：支援人員有內地認可資格　化驗所受本港法律規管<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥表示，中央會安排人員到實驗室協助做化驗工作，他們全部符合資格，但會以香港法律為基礎獲得臨時豁免。林鄭月娥說，有關人員在內地已有相關認可資格，並非不合資格而讓他們獲得豁免。她指出，3間國家級檢測機構負責病毒檢測工作，會受本港法律規管，如過程中不幸出錯，3間機構需要負責。食物及衞生局局長陳肇始重申，內地人員有經驗、受過訓練，獲得國家認可資格，他們的資格無可置疑。她說，本港有條例可由食衞局局長作出豁免，強調要與疫情競賽，在非常短時間內擴大檢測能力、符合法規，令檢測人員可協助擴大本港檢測能力，盡快在社區找出傳播鏈。<br />\n<br />\n2020-08-07 16:28:46<br />\nSource: RTHK News<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9298bb33fe72a9a1210588601989aa031234ae06","tid":2141003,"uid":345459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:54:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 垃圾政府真係威水<br />\n完美展現如何將香港最出色既一野逐件拆骨<br />\n自由<br />\n司法權<br />\n立法權<br />\n醫療體制<br />\n下次到咩？"}]}